										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">HLL Lifecare Limited (HLL), a Miniratna Central Public Sector Enterprise under the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare, Government of India, has invited applications for the recruitment of Management Trainees in various disciplines. This recruitment drive aims to fill 40 posts through a structured selection process.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Opening Date for Online Registration</strong> : 18 February 2026</li>
<li><strong>Last Date for Online Submission</strong> : 10 March 2026</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>GENERAL (UR)/OBC (Creamy Layer &amp; Non-Creamy Layer)/EWS</strong> : ₹1,000 + GST (Total ₹1,180)</li>
<li><strong>SC/ST/PwD</strong> : Exempted (No Fee)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Engineering)</strong> – 17 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Pharma)</strong> – 6 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Marketing)</strong> – 10 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Human Resources)</strong> – 2 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Social Work)</strong> – 1 Post</li>
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Data Analytics)</strong> – 1 Post</li>
<li><strong>Management Trainee (Hospital Management)</strong> – 3 Posts</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Total – 40 Posts</strong></p>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Category-wise Vacancies</strong>: UR: 14, SC: 6, ST: 3, OBC (NCL): 11, EWS: 4, PwD: 2</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit (as on 01.02.2026)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Upper Age Limit: 27 years</li>
<li>Relaxation as per Government of India rules: SC/ST – 5 years, OBC (NCL) – 3 years, PwD – 10 years (additional for SC/ST/PwD as applicable).</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification &amp; Experience</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Full-time qualifications from recognized institutions with minimum 65% aggregate marks (60% for SC/ST/PwD after relaxation). No experience required.</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Engineering</strong>: BE/B.Tech in Chemical/Mechanical/Mechatronics/Biomedical/Instrumentation/Applied Electronics/Electrical &amp; Electronics/Civil/Information Technology/Computer Science.</li>
<li><strong>Pharma</strong>: B.Pharm.</li>
<li><strong>Marketing</strong>: MBA (Marketing)/MBA (Digital Marketing)/2-year PGDBM (Marketing)/MIB/MPIB.</li>
<li><strong>Human Resources</strong>: MBA (HR)/MSW (PM&amp;IR)/2-year PGDPM/MA (PM&amp;IR)/MHRM (LLB desirable).</li>
<li><strong>Social Work</strong>: MSW (Medical and Psychiatry).</li>
<li><strong>Data Analytics</strong>: BE/B.Tech/BSc (Mathematics/Statistics) + MBA (Data Analytics).</li>
<li><strong>Hospital Management</strong>: UG in Science + MBA (Hospital Management).</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Candidates can apply for only one discipline. For detailed qualifications, refer to the official notification.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply </span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the application portal <strong><a href="https://hllmt.cbtexam.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://hllmt.cbtexam.in/</a></strong>.</li>
<li>Enter contact details and receive login credentials via SMS.</li>
<li>Fill demographic details and select the post/discipline.</li>
<li>Enter educational and work experience details (if any).</li>
<li>Upload scanned photo (&lt;100KB), signature (&lt;100KB), and certificates (.jpeg &lt;100KB or .PDF &lt;10MB).</li>
<li>Preview and modify the application if needed.</li>
<li>Pay the fee online (if applicable) and submit.</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Apply early to avoid last-minute issues. Keep a printout of the application for reference. For queries, email <a href="mailto:hllmt2026@gmail.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">hllmt2026@gmail.com</a>.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li><a href="https://hllmt.cbtexam.in/PDFDocs/Management%20Trainee%20-%2018.02.2026.pdf">Official Notification PDF</a></li>
<li><a href="https://hllmt.cbtexam.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">Apply Online</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.lifecarehll.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">HLL Lifecare Official Website</a></li>
</ol>
<p>The post <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com/2026/03/hll-lifecare-40-management-trainees-recruitment-2026/">HLL Lifecare 40 Management Trainees Recruitment 2026</a> appeared first on <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com">THE SARKARI NAUKRI</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
