										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">Konkan Railway Corporation Limited (KRCL) invites online applications for engagement as <strong>Trainee Apprentices</strong> (Graduate Apprentices and Technician (Diploma) Apprentices) for one-year training. Notification No. CO/APPR/2026/01 dated 20/02/2026 announces a total of <strong>190</strong> training slots in various engineering trades and general stream graduates.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Notification Date</strong> : 20 February 2026</li>
<li><strong>Starting Date for Online Applications</strong> : 20 February 2026</li>
<li><strong>Last Date for Online Applications</strong> : 21 March 2026</li>
<li><strong>No offline applications accepted.</strong></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>General / OBC</strong> : Rs. 100/- (Non-refundable)</li>
<li><strong>SC / ST / Female / Minorities / EWS</strong> : Nil</li>
<li><strong>Payment Mode</strong> : Online through the application portal.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Total Posts: <strong>190</strong> (Graduate Apprentices, Technician (Diploma) Apprentices, and General Stream Graduates).</p>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Trade-wise and Category-wise Breakdown</strong>:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Civil Engineering (Graduate)</strong> : 30 (UR-14, OBC-8, SC-4, ST-2, EWS-2)</li>
<li><strong>Electrical Engineering (Graduate)</strong> : 20</li>
<li><strong>Electronics Engineering (Graduate)</strong> : 10</li>
<li><strong>Mechanical Engineering (Graduate)</strong> : 20</li>
<li><strong>Civil Engineering (Diploma)</strong> : 30</li>
<li><strong>Electrical Engineering (Diploma)</strong> : 20</li>
<li><strong>Electronics Engineering (Diploma)</strong> : 10</li>
<li><strong>Mechanical Engineering (Diploma)</strong> : 20</li>
<li><strong>General Stream Graduates</strong> : 30 (Category C1)</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Category-wise Total</strong> : UR – 94, OBC(NCL) – 48, SC – 26, ST – 10, EWS – 12.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit (as on 01.01.2026)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Minimum Age</strong> : 18 years</li>
<li><strong>Maximum Age</strong> : 25 years (DOB between 01.01.2001 to 01.01.2008)</li>
<li><strong>Relaxations</strong> : 5 years for SC/ST, 3 years for OBC-NCL (subject to valid documents at verification).</li>
<li>Check official notification for complete details and additional notes.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must have passed the qualifying exam in <strong>2021, 2022, 2023, 2024, or 2025</strong>.</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Graduate Apprentices (Engineering)</strong> : BE/B.Tech in Civil, Electrical/Electronics &amp; Power (or sub-streams), Electronics/IT/Communication/CS, Mechanical/Industrial/Automobile/Production from AICTE-recognized university.</li>
<li><strong>Technician (Diploma) Apprentices</strong> : Diploma in Civil, Electrical/Electronics &amp; Power (or sub-streams), Electronics/IT/Communication/CS, Mechanical/Industrial/Automobile/Production from recognized board/university.</li>
<li><strong>General Stream Graduates</strong> : Degree in BA/BSc/BCom/BBA/BMS/BJMC/Business Studies from UGC/Central/State Govt./Technical Education Board-recognized institute.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Other Requirements</strong> — Valid NATS ID mandatory (register on NATS portal). No prior apprenticeship training under the Act allowed. Physical fitness certificate required from Government Doctor (not below Assistant Surgeon), final certification by KRCL Medical Authority. No experience needed; freshers eligible.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto">How to Apply Online for Konkan Railway Apprentices Recruitment 2026</h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official website <strong><a href="https://konkanrailway.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://konkanrailway.com/</a></strong>.</li>
<li>Go to Quick Links → Graduate Apprentice/Technician Apprentice for training in KRCL (or direct link provided in notification).</li>
<li>Register on NATS portal (nats.education.gov.in) if not done, obtain valid NATS ID.</li>
<li>Fill the online application form with personal details (as per Matric/SSC certificate), educational qualifications, etc.</li>
<li>Upload scanned photo, signature, and required documents.</li>
<li>Pay the application fee online (if applicable).</li>
<li>Submit the form and note down the registration number (sent via SMS/email).</li>
<li>Take printout for future reference.</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Tips</strong> — Apply early to avoid last-minute rush. Keep email/mobile active for updates. Read the full advertisement carefully before applying. No changes to email/mobile allowed later.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto">Important Links</h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Official Notification PDF : <a href="https://konkanrailway.com/sites/default/files/2026-02/Notification_Trainee_Apprentice_2026.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://konkanrailway.com/sites/default/files/2026-02/Notification_Trainee_Apprentice_2026.pdf</a></li>
<li>Apply Online : <a href="https://konkanrailway.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://konkanrailway.com/</a> (Quick Links section) or <a href="https://wps.konkanrailway.com/nats" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://wps.konkanrailway.com/nats</a></li>
<li>NATS Portal Registration : <a href="https://nats.education.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://nats.education.gov.in</a></li>
<li>KRCL Official Website : <a href="https://konkanrailway.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://konkanrailway.com</a></li>
</ol>
<p>The post <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com/2026/02/konkan-railway-recruitment-2026/">Konkan Railway Recruitment 2026 – 190 Posts</a> appeared first on <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com">THE SARKARI NAUKRI</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
