										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">Hindustan Petroleum Corporation Limited (HPCL) has released a major recruitment notification for Officers, Junior Executives, Engineers, and other profiles in February 2026. The official advertisement (Advt. No. HPCL/OPEN/HR/3/2025-26) details vacancies for various positions, with the total number of posts widely reported as 731 across freshers and experienced categories.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Notification Release Date</strong>: February 2026</li>
<li><strong>Online Application Start Date</strong>: 25 February 2026 (from 13:00 hrs)</li>
<li><strong>Last Date to Apply Online</strong>: 25 March 2026 (up to 23:59 hrs)</li>
<li><strong>Tentative CBT Date</strong>: 03 May 2026 (subject to change)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>For UR/OBCNC/EWS</strong>: ₹1180 (including ₹1000 + 18% GST + payment gateway charges)</li>
<li><strong>For SC/ST/PwBD</strong>: Exempted</li>
<li><strong>Payment Mode</strong>: Online via Debit/Credit Card, UPI, Net Banking</li>
<li>Note: Fee is non-refundable.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">HPCL has announced <strong>731 vacancies</strong> for various disciplines, including both freshers (SIT criteria) and experienced professionals.</p>
<h4 dir="auto">Key Positions for Freshers (Indicative)</h4>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Junior Executive – Mechanical: 207</li>
<li>Junior Executive – Electrical: 117</li>
<li>Junior Executive – Civil: 19</li>
<li>Junior Executive – Chemical: 27</li>
<li>Mechanical Engineer: 72</li>
<li>Electrical Engineer: 37</li>
<li>Civil Engineer: 17</li>
<li>Chemical Engineer: 15</li>
<li>Officer – Finance (CA): 30</li>
<li>Officer – Finance (CMA): 4</li>
<li>Officer – Finance (MBA): 4</li>
<li>Officer – HR: 6</li>
<li>Officer – IS: 20</li>
<li>Junior Executive – Quality Control: 12</li>
<li>Junior Executive – Fire &amp; Safety: 16</li>
<li>Junior Executive Assistant: 10</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit (as on 25 March 2026)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Freshers</strong>: Maximum 25 years (27 years for some positions like Finance/HR Officers)</li>
<li><strong>Experienced</strong>: Varies by post (up to 45 years for senior roles)</li>
<li><strong>Relaxations</strong>: As per Government norms – 5 years for SC/ST, 3 years for OBCNC, 10 years for PwBD (additional for combined categories), ex-servicemen, etc. Additional relaxation up to 2 years for relevant experience in some cases.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Eligibility Criteria</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Educational Qualification</strong>:
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Engineering posts: Full-time regular B.E./B.Tech or Diploma in relevant discipline (Mechanical, Electrical, Civil, Chemical, etc.) with minimum 65% marks (55% for SC/ST/PwBD).</li>
<li>Finance: Qualified CA/CMA with graduation; MBA for specific roles.</li>
<li>HR/IS/Fire &amp; Safety: Relevant degree/diploma/qualification.</li>
<li>Experience: 0 years for freshers; 3–16+ years for experienced/senior roles (post-qualifying degree).</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Minimum Marks</strong>: 65% in qualifying exam for UR/OBCNC/EWS (55% for reserved categories); specific for CA/CMA.</li>
<li>Candidates must be Indian nationals. Final-year students (2025-26 passing) may apply for certain posts.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official website: <a href="https://www.hindustanpetroleum.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://www.hindustanpetroleum.com</a></li>
<li>Go to <strong>Careers</strong> &gt; <strong>Current Openings</strong></li>
<li>Find <strong>Recruitment of Officers &#8211; Feb 2026</strong></li>
<li>Read the detailed advertisement carefully</li>
<li>Register and fill the online application form</li>
<li>Upload photo, signature, and required documents</li>
<li>Pay the application fee (if applicable)</li>
<li>Submit and take a printout of the confirmation page</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Keep a valid email ID and mobile number active for updates. Apply early to avoid last-minute issues.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Official Notification PDF: <a href="https://www.hindustanpetroleum.com/documents/pdf/Recruitment%20of%20Officers-%20Feb%202026_details.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://www.hindustanpetroleum.com/documents/pdf/Recruitment%20of%20Officers-%20Feb%202026_details.pdf</a></li>
</ul>
