										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">The All India Institute of Medical Sciences (AIIMS), New Delhi has released the AIIMS NORCET 10 Recruitment Notification 2026 for the post of Nursing Officer. This is a golden opportunity for nursing professionals to join prestigious AIIMS institutions across India. A total of 2551 posts are announced under the Nursing Officer Recruitment Common Eligibility Test (NORCET)-10.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Notification Release Date: 24 February 2026</li>
<li>Online Application Start Date: 24 February 2026</li>
<li>Last Date to Apply Online: 16 March 2026 (05:00 PM)</li>
<li>Last Date for Submission of NOC (if applicable): 20 March 2026</li>
<li>Stage-I (Prelims) Exam Date: 11 April 2026</li>
<li>Stage-II (Mains) Exam Date: 30 April 2026</li>
<li>Mains Result (Tentative): Around 11 May 2026</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>General / OBC: ₹3000/-</li>
<li>SC / ST / EWS: ₹2400/-</li>
<li>PwBD (Persons with Benchmark Disabilities): Exempted (No Fee)</li>
<li>Payment Mode: Online through Debit Card, Credit Card, Net Banking, etc.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<p><span style="color: #ff9900;"><strong>Nursing Officer (Group B)</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Total Number of Posts</strong> &#8211; 2551</p>
<ul>
<li>UR (Unreserved) &#8211; 1113 Posts</li>
<li>OBC (NCL) &#8211; 643 Posts</li>
<li>SC &#8211; 375 Posts</li>
<li>ST &#8211; 194 Posts</li>
<li>EWS &#8211; 226 Posts</li>
<li>Grand Total &#8211; 2551 Posts</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit (as on crucial date)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Minimum Age: 18 Years</li>
<li>Maximum Age: 30 Years</li>
<li>Age Relaxation: As per government rules (SC/ST – 5 years, OBC – 3 years, PwBD – 10 years, etc.)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must possess one of the following:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>B.Sc. (Hons.) Nursing / B.Sc. Nursing from an Indian Nursing Council / State Nursing Council recognized Institute or University <strong>OR</strong></li>
<li>Post Basic B.Sc. Nursing <strong>OR</strong></li>
<li>Diploma in General Nursing Midwifery (GNM) from a recognized institution + Minimum 2 years of experience as a Registered Nurse/Midwife in a minimum 50-bedded hospital (after passing GNM)</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must be registered as Nurses &amp; Midwife with State / Indian Nursing Council.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply Online for AIIMS NORCET 10 2026</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official website: <a href="https://aiimsexams.ac.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://aiimsexams.ac.in/</a></li>
<li>Click on the &#8220;NORCET-10&#8221; or &#8220;Recruitment&#8221; link.</li>
<li>Register yourself by providing basic details (Name, Email, Mobile, etc.).</li>
<li>Login and fill the online application form carefully.</li>
<li>Upload scanned copies of photograph, signature, and required documents.</li>
<li>Pay the application fee (if applicable).</li>
<li>Submit the form and take a printout of the confirmation page for future reference.</li>
</ol>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<p>Apply Online: <a href="https://www.aiimsexams.ac.in/advertisement/699d90c3a5c5ab7d59ac721b">Click here</a><br />
Official Notification PDF: <a href="https://rrpdocuments.aiimsexams.ac.in/1771933787527-856734394.pdf?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAVRUVRLXWMSLVSAP7%2F20260225%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260225T160201Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=18000&amp;X-Amz-Signature=a2d2adc6dd5b1cddb889a545361742c50f6bef0113057578c02bc50dd223fcd5&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;response-content-type=application%2Fpdf">Click here</a><br />
Official Website: <a href="https://www.aiimsexams.ac.in/">Click here </a></p>
