										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">The Central Selection Board of Constables (CSBC), Bihar, has released the official notification for the recruitment of Constable (Operator) posts in the Bihar Police Radio (Technical) Cadre under Advertisement No. 02/2026. This is a great opportunity for 12th-pass candidates seeking a government job in Bihar Police with a focus on operator roles.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Notification Release Date: <strong>February 23, 2026</strong></li>
<li>Application Start Date: <strong>01 March 2026</strong></li>
<li>Last Date to Apply Online: <strong>31 March 2026</strong></li>
<li>Last Date for Fee Payment: <strong>31 March 2026</strong></li>
<li>Exam Date: To be announced later</li>
<li>Admit Card: Before the exam</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>For All Categories (including SC/ST/EWS/BC): <strong>Rs. 100/-</strong></li>
<li>Payment Mode: Online through Debit Card, Credit Card, Net Banking, UPI, or other available modes (additional bank charges may apply).</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<p dir="auto"><span style="color: #ff9900;"><strong>Constable (Operator)</strong></span> in Bihar Police Radio (Technical) Cadre <strong>Total Vacancies:</strong> <strong>993 Posts</strong></p>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Category-wise Reservation:</strong></p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Unreserved (UR): <strong>408</strong></li>
<li>Economically Weaker Section (EWS): <strong>99</strong></li>
<li>Extremely Backward Class (EBC): <strong>175</strong></li>
<li>Backward Class (BC): <strong>113</strong> (including 02 for BC Creamy Layer)</li>
<li>Backward Class Women (BCW): <strong>31</strong></li>
<li>Scheduled Caste (SC): <strong>157</strong></li>
<li>Scheduled Tribe (ST): <strong>10</strong></li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">(Note: Horizontal reservations apply for women, ex-servicemen, etc., as per rules. 338 vacancies are reserved for women candidates overall.)</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Age calculated as on <strong>01 August 2026</strong> (minimum) and <strong>01 August 2021</strong> (maximum, with relaxations applied).</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Minimum Age: <strong>18 Years</strong></li>
<li>Maximum Age:
<ul dir="auto">
<li>UR / BC: <strong>25 Years</strong></li>
<li>EBC: <strong>27 Years</strong></li>
<li>SC / ST / Transgender: <strong>30 Years</strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Age Relaxation: Additional for Bihar domicile women (35% horizontal), ex-servicemen, freedom fighters&#8217; dependents, etc., as per Bihar government rules.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must have passed <strong>Intermediate (10+2)</strong> or equivalent from a recognized board with:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>At least <strong>50% marks</strong> in Hindi and one of the subjects (History, Geography, Economics).</li>
<li>For SC/ST/BC/EBC/BCW categories: <strong>45% marks</strong> in the above. Subjects focus on Hindi, History, Geography, and Economics at the Intermediate level.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Physical Standards</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Height (Male):</strong> UR/EBC/BC: <strong>165 cm</strong>; SC/ST: <strong>160 cm</strong> (with chest 81-86 cm for UR/EBC/BC and 79-84 cm for SC/ST, minimum 5 cm expansion).</li>
<li><strong>Height (Female):</strong><strong>155 cm</strong> (minimum weight <strong>48 kg</strong>; no chest measurement).</li>
<li>Relaxations apply for reserved categories and transgender candidates as per rules.</li>
<li>Physical Efficiency Test (PET) is qualifying in nature.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official website: <strong><a href="https://csbc.bihar.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://csbc.bihar.gov.in</a></strong></li>
<li>Click on the link for Constable (Operator) Advt. No. 02/2026 and register using your mobile number/email.</li>
<li>Fill in personal, educational, and category details in the online form.</li>
<li>Upload scanned photograph (15-25 KB, JPG format), signature, and required certificates.</li>
<li>Pay the application fee online.</li>
<li>Submit the form and take a printout of the acknowledgment for future reference.</li>
<li>Apply only once; multiple applications will lead to rejection.</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Ensure all details match your certificates to avoid disqualification.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Official Notification PDF: <a href="https://csbc.bihar.gov.in/Advt/Advt-02-2026-Constable(Operator).pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://csbc.bihar.gov.in/Advt/Advt-02-2026-Constable(Operator).pdf</a></li>
<li>Apply Online: <a href="https://csbc.bihar.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://csbc.bihar.gov.in</a> (or direct link from notice: <a href="https://apply-csbc.com/csbc_ct_operator_2_26_final/applicationIndex" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://apply-csbc.com/csbc_ct_operator_2_26_final/applicationIndex</a>)</li>
<li>Official Website: <a href="https://csbc.bihar.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://csbc.bihar.gov.in</a></li>
</ul>
