										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">State Bank of India (SBI) has released the official notification for the recruitment of Specialist Cadre Officers (SCO) in areas like Information Systems (IS) Audit and Chartered Accountant &#8211; Internal Audit on regular and contractual basis. This is under Advertisement No: CRPD/SCO/2025-26/27. A total of 116 posts are announced (including backlog vacancies).</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Notification Release Date: 23 February 2026</li>
<li>Online Registration / Application Start Date: 23 February 2026</li>
<li>Last Date for Online Registration &amp; Application: 15 March 2026</li>
<li>Last Date for Payment of Application Fee: 15 March 2026</li>
<li>Cut-off Date for Eligibility (Age, Qualification, Experience): 31 January 2026</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>General / EWS / OBC: ₹750 (Non-refundable)</li>
<li>SC / ST / PwBD: No Fee (Exempted)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Total Vacancies: 116 Posts</strong> (Regular + Backlog, provisional and may vary)</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Assistant Vice President (IS Audit)</strong> – Contractual: 12 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Deputy Manager (IS Audit)</strong> – Regular (MMGS-II): 43 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Deputy Manager (Chartered Accountant &#8211; Internal Audit)</strong> – Regular (MMGS-II): 61 Posts</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit (as on 31/01/2026)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Assistant Vice President (IS Audit): Minimum 27 years – Maximum 45 years</li>
<li>Deputy Manager (IS Audit): Minimum 25 years – Maximum 35 years</li>
<li>Deputy Manager (Chartered Accountant &#8211; Internal Audit): Minimum 21 years – Maximum 35 years</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Age Relaxation</strong> (as per Government norms):</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>OBC (Non-Creamy Layer): 3 years</li>
<li>SC / ST: 5 years</li>
<li>PwBD (UR/EWS): 10 years; OBC: 13 years; SC/ST: 15 years (Other relaxations as applicable; refer to detailed advertisement)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Assistant Vice President (IS Audit) &amp; Deputy Manager (IS Audit)</strong>: Essential: B.Sc./B.E./B.Tech in Computer Science/Software Engineering/IT/Electronics or equivalent (min. 50%); OR BCA/MCA; OR M.Tech/M.Sc in relevant disciplines (min. 50%). Desirable: Certifications like CISA, CISSP, CISM, DISA, ISO 27001 Lead Auditor, CEH, GIAC (valid on last date of registration).</li>
<li><strong>Deputy Manager (Chartered Accountant &#8211; Internal Audit)</strong>: Chartered Accountant (C.A.) with active membership of ICAI. Preferred: CISA, DISA.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Teaching/training experience will <strong>not</strong> be counted.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Experience (Post-qualification, as on 31/01/2026)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Assistant Vice President (IS Audit)</strong>: Minimum 6 years in BFSI/IT/Information Security Consultancy, including at least 3 years in IS Audit/Cyber Security Audit/Information Security Consultancy.</li>
<li><strong>Deputy Manager (IS Audit)</strong>: Minimum 3 years in BFSI/IT/Information Security Consultancy, including at least 2 years in IS Audit/Cyber Security Audit/Information Security Consultancy.</li>
<li><strong>Deputy Manager (Chartered Accountant &#8211; Internal Audit)</strong>: Minimum 1 year post-qualification in Statutory/Internal/Concurrent Audit in Bank or with CA firm engaged in such audits.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official SBI careers website: <a href="https://sbi.bank.in/web/careers/current-openings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://sbi.bank.in/web/careers/current-openings</a></li>
<li>Scroll to the relevant advertisement (CRPD/SCO/2025-26/27) and click on &#8220;Apply Online&#8221;.</li>
<li>Register with valid email ID and mobile number.</li>
<li>Fill the online application form carefully.</li>
<li>Upload required documents: Resume, ID proof, age proof, PwBD certificate (if applicable), educational certificates, certifications, experience proofs, Biodata, photo &amp; signature (in specified formats/sizes: photo 20-50 KB 200&#215;230 px; signature 10-20 KB 140&#215;60 px; documents ≤500 KB).</li>
<li>Pay the application fee online (if applicable).</li>
<li>Submit the form and take printout of application &amp; e-receipt for future reference.</li>
<li>Edit option available up to 3 times before final submission.</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must ensure all details are correct; multiple applications lead to last valid one retained. No hard copy needed.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Official Notification PDF: <a href="https://sbi.bank.in/documents/77530/52947104/23022026_ADV+CRPD_SCO_2025-26_27_23022026.pdf/d205d3d0-ecc5-9cdc-9637-9f384d830cb0?t=1771825373224" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">Download Advertisement</a></li>
<li>Apply Online: <a href="https://sbi.bank.in/web/careers/current-openings" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://sbi.bank.in/web/careers/current-openings</a> (Click on the respective link)</li>
<li>SBI Careers Page: <a href="https://sbi.bank.in/web/careers" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://sbi.bank.in/web/careers</a></li>
</ul>
