										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">The National Informatics Centre (NIC), under the Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology, Government of India, has released a short notification for the direct recruitment of Scientist ‘B’ (Group ‘A’, Gazetted) posts. A total of 243 vacancies have been announced in Pay Level-10.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Short Notification Release Date: Early February 2026 (around 5-6 February 2026)</li>
<li>Detailed Notification Availability: Tentatively within 10 days from GATE-2026 result announcement</li>
<li>Online Application Start Date: To be announced with detailed notification</li>
<li>Last Date for Online Applications: To be announced with detailed notification</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Application fee details will be provided in the detailed notification on the official website. Typically for such government recruitments, fees are category-based (e.g., exempted for SC/ST/PwBD/women, nominal for others), payable online.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<p><strong>Scientist ‘B’ (Group ‘A’, Gazetted)</strong></p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Total Vacancies</strong>: 243 Posts</li>
<li><strong>Category-wise Reservation</strong> (as per short notice):
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Unreserved (UR): 100</li>
<li>Schedule Caste (SC): 36</li>
<li>Schedule Tribe (ST): 18</li>
<li>Other Backward Class (OBC-NCL): 65</li>
<li>Economically Weaker Section (EWS): 24</li>
<li>Persons with Benchmark Disabilities (PwBD) (Horizontal): 10</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Age limit details will be specified in the full advertisement. Previous similar recruitments often set upper age at 30 years for general category, with relaxations for reserved categories (e.g., 5 years for SC/ST, 3 years for OBC).</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must possess one of the following qualifications in relevant fields (Electronics, Electronics &amp; Communication, Computer Science, IT, etc., single or in combination):</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Bachelor’s Degree in Engineering / Technology (B.E./B.Tech)</li>
<li>DOEACC B-Level</li>
<li>Associate Member of Institute of Engineers / Graduate Institute of Electronics and Telecommunication Engineers</li>
<li>Master’s Degree in Science (M.Sc)</li>
<li>Master’s Degree in Computer Applications (MCA)</li>
<li>Master’s Degree in Engineering / Technology (M.E./M.Tech)</li>
<li>Master’s Degree in Philosophy (M.Phil)</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Essential Requirement</strong>: Valid GATE score in 2024 / 2025 / 2026 in one of the following papers:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Computer Science and Information Technology (CS)</li>
<li>Electronics &amp; Communication Engineering (EC)</li>
<li>Data Science and Artificial Intelligence (DA)</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Final eligibility and exact qualifying disciplines will be detailed in the full notification.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official NIC recruitment website: <a href="https://recruitment.nic.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://recruitment.nic.in</a></li>
<li>Wait for the detailed advertisement link to appear (expected soon after GATE-2026 results).</li>
<li>Register and fill the online application form with personal, educational, and GATE details.</li>
<li>Upload required documents (photo, signature, certificates, GATE scorecard).</li>
<li>Pay the application fee (if applicable) through online mode.</li>
<li>Submit the form and take a printout for reference.</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Applications will only be accepted online. No offline mode is available.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Official Short Notification / Details: <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/NIC26-1.pdf">https://thesarkarinaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/NIC26-1.pdf</a></li>
<li>Apply Online: Available soon at <a href="https://recruitment.nic.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://recruitment.nic.in</a></li>
<li>Official NIC Website: <a href="https://www.nic.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://www.nic.in</a></li>
<li>GATE Information: Refer to GATE official portal for scores</li>
</ul>
