					<description><![CDATA[<p>The Goa Staff Selection Commission (GSSC) has released Advertisement No. 2 of Year 2026 for filling up 722 Group C vacancies through online applications. This recruitment covers posts like Police Constable, Forest Guard, Warden, Matron, and others, offering stable careers under the Government of Goa. Important Dates Advertisement Date: 20 February 2026 Starting Date for ... </p>
