										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">Chittaranjan National Cancer Institute (CNCI), Kolkata, an autonomous institute under the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare, Government of India, has released a notification for the recruitment of Staff Nurse posts on a contractual basis through a manpower outsourcing agency. This is a great opportunity for qualified nursing professionals to join a premier cancer care institution.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Date &amp; time of commencement of Applications: <strong>21.02.2026 from 10:00 AM</strong></li>
<li>Last date &amp; time of Applications: <strong>02.03.2026 up to 05:00 PM</strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">No application fee is mentioned in the official advertisement.</p>
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Post Name</strong>: Staff Nurse</li>
<li><strong>Number of Posts</strong>: <strong>40</strong></li>
<li><strong>Remuneration</strong>: <strong>₹30,000/-</strong> per month (paid through the outsourcing agency; PF, ESIC, and other statutory benefits as applicable)</li>
</ul>
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Maximum Age: <strong>35 Years</strong></li>
<li>Age and experience are reckoned as on the closing date (02.03.2026).</li>
<li><strong>Relaxation</strong>: Equivalent to the years of experience beyond essential criteria for candidates with higher experience.</li>
</ul>
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must meet one of the following:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>General Nursing &amp; Midwifery (GNM) plus Diploma in Oncology Nursing <strong>OR</strong></li>
<li>Basic or Post-Basic B.Sc (Nursing) <strong>OR</strong></li>
<li>General Nursing &amp; Midwifery plus two years of experience in a minimum 50-bedded hospital after acquiring the above qualification.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Additional Requirements</strong>:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Candidates must be registered with the Indian Nursing Council / State Nursing Council.</li>
<li>All qualifications must be recognized by law.</li>
<li>Relevant experience and qualifications are mandatory.</li>
</ul>
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply</span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Interested and eligible candidates can apply through the following modes:</p>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Fill and submit the online Google Form at: <strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeWG04O7tPhMMKRQKS2721OPuSkLuEjuiV513T--AFY5eQ0bQ/viewform?usp=header" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeWG04O7tPhMMKRQKS2721OPuSkLuEjuiV513T&#8211;AFY5eQ0bQ/viewform?usp=header</a></strong></li>
<li>Alternatively, send duly filled applications in the prescribed format via email to: <strong><a href="mailto:recruitment.cncik@gmail.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">recruitment.cncik@gmail.com</a></strong></li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Candidates should:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Attach recent passport-size photograph (not older than 3 months).</li>
<li>Provide complete details including name, DOB, category, qualifications, registration number, etc.</li>
<li>Visit the official website <strong><a href="http://www.cnci.ac.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">www.cnci.ac.in</a></strong> regularly for updates, corrigendum, or addendum.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Incomplete applications will be rejected. No interim queries will be entertained.</p>
<h3 dir="auto">Important Links</h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Official Advertisement PDF: <strong><a href="https://cnci.ac.in/backend/public/uploads/2026/02/21/Advt.%20Staff%20Nurse_DK%20_02-2026.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://cnci.ac.in/backend/public/uploads/2026/02/21/Advt.%20Staff%20Nurse_DK%20_02-2026.pdf</a></strong></li>
<li>Online Application Form: <strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeWG04O7tPhMMKRQKS2721OPuSkLuEjuiV513T--AFY5eQ0bQ/viewform?usp=header" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeWG04O7tPhMMKRQKS2721OPuSkLuEjuiV513T&#8211;AFY5eQ0bQ/viewform?usp=header</a></strong></li>
<li>Official Website: <strong><a href="https://cnci.ac.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://cnci.ac.in/</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p>The post <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com/2026/02/chittaranjan-national-cancer-institute-cnci-kolkata-recruitment-2026-40-staff-nurse-posts/">Chittaranjan National Cancer Institute (CNCI) Kolkata Recruitment 2026 &#8211; 40 Staff Nurse Posts</a> appeared first on <a href="https://thesarkarinaukri.com">THE SARKARI NAUKRI</a>.</p>
