										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">The Delhi Subordinate Services Selection Board (DSSSB) has released the notification for Combined Examinations 2026 vide Advertisement No. 01/2026 dated 20 February 2026. Online applications are invited for 911 vacancies in posts including Assistant Engineer (Civil), Junior Engineer (Civil), Legal Assistant, and Grade-II (DASS)/Assistant Section Officer (ASO) in various departments under Government of NCT of Delhi.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Dates</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Notification Release Date</strong> — 20 February 2026</li>
<li><strong>Online Application Start Date</strong> — 24 February 2026 (12:00 Noon)</li>
<li><strong>Last Date to Apply Online</strong> — 25 March 2026 (till 11:59 PM)</li>
<li><strong>Exam Date</strong> — To be announced later</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Application Fee</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>UR / OBC / EWS</strong> — ₹100/-</li>
<li><strong>SC / ST / PwD / Female Candidates</strong> — No Fee (Exempted)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Vacancy Details</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Total Posts</strong> — <strong>911</strong></li>
<li>Posts include:
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Legal Assistant</strong> — 10</li>
<li><strong>Assistant Engineer (Civil)</strong> — 33</li>
<li><strong>Junior Engineer (Civil)</strong> — 281</li>
<li><strong>Grade-II (GNCTDSS) / Assistant Section Officer (ASO)</strong> — 587</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Grand Total: 911</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Educational Qualification</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>For Assistant Engineer (Civil) / Junior Engineer (Civil)</strong> — Degree / Diploma in Civil Engineering from a recognized university/institution.</li>
<li><strong>For Legal Assistant</strong> — Degree in Law (LLB) from a recognized university + relevant experience (as specified).</li>
<li><strong>For Assistant Section Officer (ASO) / Grade-II</strong> — Bachelor’s Degree from a recognized university.</li>
<li>(Post-specific qualifications apply; check detailed notification for exact requirements including NCVT/ITIs if any for technical posts.)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Age Limit (as on 25/03/2026)</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Minimum Age</strong> — 18-21 Years (post-wise)</li>
<li><strong>Maximum Age</strong> — 30-35 Years (post-wise)</li>
<li><strong>Age Relaxation</strong>:
<ul dir="auto">
<li>SC/ST — 5 years</li>
<li>OBC — 3 years</li>
<li>PwD — 10 years (additional relaxations as per rules)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Pay Scale / Salary</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Selected candidates will get pay as per <strong>7th Pay Commission</strong> levels:
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Assistant Engineer — Level 9/10 (approx. ₹53,100 – ₹1,77,500)</li>
<li>Junior Engineer — Level 6/7 (approx. ₹35,400 – ₹1,12,400)</li>
<li>Legal Assistant / ASO — Level 6 to 8 (approx. ₹35,400 – ₹1,42,400)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>(Exact pay matrix and allowances as per Delhi Govt norms)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">How to Apply</span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official website: <a href="https://dsssb.delhi.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://dsssb.delhi.gov.in</a> or application portal <a href="https://dsssbonline.nic.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://dsssbonline.nic.in</a></li>
<li>Register using valid email and mobile number (Aadhaar-linked preferred).</li>
<li>Fill the online application form carefully with personal, educational, and experience details.</li>
<li>Upload scanned photo, signature, and required documents.</li>
<li>Pay the application fee (if applicable) online.</li>
<li>Submit the form and take a printout for future reference.</li>
</ol>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>No offline/hard copy applications accepted.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;">Important Links</span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Official Notification PDF</strong>: <a href="https://dsssb.delhi.gov.in/sites/default/files/DSSSB/circulars-orders/final_advt_01-2026_1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">Download Here</a></li>
<li><strong>Apply Online</strong>: <a href="https://dsssbonline.nic.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://dsssbonline.nic.in</a></li>
<li><strong>Official Website</strong>: <a href="https://dsssb.delhi.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://dsssb.delhi.gov.in</a></li>
</ul>
