										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="auto">Employees State Insurance Corporation (ESIC) has released a recruitment notification (Advertisement No. 03 of 2026) for filling up 19 posts of Teaching Faculty (Professor, Associate Professor) and Senior Residents in various Super Specialty Departments on a contract basis at ESIC Medical College &amp; Hospital, Indore, Madhya Pradesh.</p>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Important Dates</strong></span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Notification Release Date</strong> — 20 February 2026</li>
<li><strong>Last Date for Receipt of Application</strong> — 02 March 2026</li>
<li><strong>Date of Interview</strong> — 12 March 2026</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Application Fee</strong></span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>General / OBC</strong> — Rs. 500/-</li>
<li><strong>SC / ST</strong> — NIL (Exempted)</li>
<li><strong>Payment Mode</strong> — As prescribed in the official notification (likely Demand Draft in favor of the designated authority).</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Vacancy Details</strong></span></h3>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Teaching Faculty / Senior Residents</strong> <strong>Total Posts</strong> — <strong>19</strong></p>
<p dir="auto">Posts include:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li>Professor (Cardiology, Medical Oncology, Surgical Oncology, Urology)</li>
<li>Associate Professor (Cardiology, Medical Oncology, Nephrology, Surgical Oncology, Urology)</li>
<li>Senior Resident (Cardiology, Medical Oncology, Nephrology, Surgical Oncology, Urology)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Educational Qualification</strong></span></h3>
<p dir="auto">Candidates must possess qualifications and experience strictly as per the latest <strong>National Medical Commission (NMC)</strong> guidelines (erstwhile MCI) for the respective posts:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Professor / Associate Professor</strong> — MBBS + MD/MS/DM/MCh or equivalent in relevant super specialty, plus required teaching/research experience as per NMC norms.</li>
<li><strong>Senior Resident</strong> — MBBS + MD/MS/DNB or equivalent in relevant specialty as per NMC guidelines.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Age Limit</strong></span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Maximum Age</strong> — 69 Years (as on closing date)</li>
<li>Age relaxation applicable as per Government of India norms for SC/ST/OBC/PwD/Ex-Servicemen categories.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Pay Scale / Salary</strong></span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Professor</strong> — Rs. 1,23,100/- (Level 13)</li>
<li><strong>Associate Professor</strong> — Rs. 78,800/- (Level 12)</li>
<li><strong>Senior Resident</strong> — Rs. 67,700/- (Level 11)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>How to Apply</strong></span></h3>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Visit the official ESIC website — <a href="https://esic.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://esic.gov.in</a></li>
<li>Download the official notification (Advertisement No. 03 of 2026) and application format.</li>
<li>Read the notification carefully and check eligibility.</li>
<li>Fill the application form with accurate details.</li>
<li>Attach self-attested copies of required documents (educational certificates, experience proofs, age proof, category certificate if applicable, recent photograph, etc.).</li>
<li>Pay the application fee (if applicable) via Demand Draft or as specified.</li>
<li>Send the completed application form along with all enclosures to the address mentioned in the notification (likely Dean/Director, ESIC Medical College &amp; Hospital, Indore) via Speed Post/Registered Post.</li>
<li>Ensure the application reaches the office on or before <strong>02 March 2026</strong>. Late/incomplete applications will be rejected.</li>
</ol>
<hr />
<h3 dir="auto"><span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Important Links</strong></span></h3>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Official Notification</strong> —  <a href="https://esic.gov.in/attachments/recruitmentfile/Advertisement_No_03_of_2026_Recruitment_of_Teaching_Faculty_Senior_Residents_for_Super_Specialty_Departments_on_contract_basis_at_ESIC_Medical_College_amp_Hospital_Indore_MP_1771579078.pdf">Click Here</a></li>
